  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::TombOfServilii.TopicData
  topicTitle: What is it?
  contentText: The Tomb of the Servilii is a historic monument located along the
    ancient Via Appia in Rome. It represents a typical Roman aristocratic family
    tomb, constructed during the late Republic and early Empire to house the remains
    of the distinguished Servilia family.
  narrationClip: {fileID: 0}
  subtitleText: The Tomb of the Servilii is a historic monument located along the
    ancient Via Appia in Rome.
